OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776942175
OL,3,CDamning report into government IT
OL,4,Cproject raises multiple failures
OL,6,FA report into Guernsey's IT programme
OL,7,Fhas found it failed across several key
OL,8,Fareas, resulting in a "waste" of more
OL,9,Fthan #21 million of public funds.
OL,11,FThe States-run MyGov programme was a
OL,12,Fgroup of projects aimed at delivering
OL,13,Fcustomer and workforce improvements.
OL,15,FThe initiative was targeted at the
OL,16,Fdigitalisation of government services
OL,17,Fand delivering modern, user-focused
OL,18,Fservices and financial savings.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776942175
OL,3,CDamning report into government IT
OL,4,Cproject raises multiple failures
OL,6,FThe investigation into MyGov, which
OL,7,Fwas announced in November 2025, found
OL,8,Fthat the programme suffered from weak
OL,9,Fleadership, "poor financial control",
OL,10,Fand an "over-reliance" on external
OL,11,Fcontractors such as Agilisys, which
OL,12,Fweakened security.
OL,14,FBoley Smillie, Chief Executive at the
OL,15,FStates of Guernsey, told ITV News:
OL,16,F"It's not a good story. #21 million in
OL,17,Ftotal was spent for very little return
OL,18,Fin terms of benefits.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776942175
OL,3,CDamning report into government IT
OL,4,Cproject raises multiple failures
OL,6,F"Arguably, even those benefits that
OL,7,Fwere claimed at the end of the project
OL,8,Fhave a tenuous link to the program
OL,9,Fitself on the scale of investment."
OL,11,FIn the report, Mr Smillie says there
OL,12,Fwas a culture in which challenges were
OL,13,Fdiscouraged, and those who did raise
OL,14,Fconcerns were seen as "resistant" or
OL,15,F"unhelpful" and even excluded from
OL,16,Fsome discussions.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776942175
OL,3,CDamning report into government IT
OL,4,Cproject raises multiple failures
OL,6,FHe adds that this tense environment
OL,7,Feven led to the loss of experienced
OL,8,Fstaff, with others citing low morale
OL,9,Fand lack of confidence, amid the
OL,10,Fbackdrop of the challenging Covid
OL,11,Fpandemic.
OL,13,FThe report also found that MyGov
OL,14,Flacked a clear definition, with
OL,15,Fprojects often "rebranded" and
OL,16,F"rescoped".
OL,18,FThere were also concerns over the
OL,19,Fnumber of individuals involved in the
OL,20,Fprojects, with more than 20 boards and
OL,21,Fgroups outlined in documentation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776942175
OL,3,CDamning report into government IT
OL,4,Cproject raises multiple failures
OL,6,FA number of reforms have been proposed
OL,7,Fin the report, which include
OL,8,Fleadership changes, independent
OL,9,Fexpertise to oversee the delivery of
OL,10,Fall major projects, and improved
OL,11,Ftransparency by publishing a new
OL,12,Fannual report on updates to major
OL,13,Fprogrammes.
OL,15,FTo improve accountability, it also
OL,16,Frecommends introducing Chief Officers
OL,17,Faligned to Principal Committees.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776942175
OL,3,CDamning report into government IT
OL,4,Cproject raises multiple failures
OL,6,FEarlier this year, another government
OL,7,FIT project aimed at digitising health
OL,8,Fservices came under fierce scrutiny
OL,9,Fafter it was revealed that millions of
OL,10,Fpounds in extra funding would not be
OL,11,Fenough to cover the work.
OL,13,FIn a statement announcing the findings
OL,14,Fof the MyGov report, Mr Smilie said:
OL,15,F"This report shines a harsh light on
OL,16,Fthe MyGov programme, highlighting
OL,17,Fsignificant issues that need
OL,18,Faddressing. However, these findings do
OL,19,Fnot define the civil service as a
OL,20,Fwhole.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776942175
OL,3,CDamning report into government IT
OL,4,Cproject raises multiple failures
OL,6,F"The majority of our public servants
OL,7,Fare professional, highly effective,
OL,8,Fand deeply committed to serving our
OL,9,Fcommunity. By addressing the issues
OL,10,Fwithin MyGov, it is my belief we can
OL,11,Fthen start to build public trust and
OL,12,Fhighlight the dedication and values
OL,13,Fthat define the rest of the civil
OL,14,Fservice.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776942175
OL,3,CDamning report into government IT
OL,4,Cproject raises multiple failures
OL,6,F"I will now take the actions needed to
OL,7,Fensure these failures are never
OL,8,Frepeated. Several of the issues seen
OL,9,Fin MyGov have been repeated across
OL,10,Fother transformational programmes. The
OL,11,Ftime for analysis has passed; the
OL,12,Ffocus now is on action. Some changes
OL,13,Fhave already been implemented, others
OL,14,Fare underway.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1776942175
OL,3,CDamning report into government IT
OL,4,Cproject raises multiple failures
OL,6,F"In the face of such a significant
OL,7,Ffailure, I want to assure the
OL,8,Fcommunity that this review was not an
OL,9,Fexercise in "lessons learned" but
OL,10,Frather it identifies where tangible
OL,11,Faction is needed, and will be
OL,12,Fdelivered."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
